{"id": "7c6642e1", "created": "2026-05-03T18:25:46.068809", "analysis": {"root_cause": "缓存机制缺失或缓存键设计不当，导致相同聚合计算的请求无法复用缓存，每次都触发全量重新计算", "error_type": "design", "confidence": 0.92, "suggestion": "1. 实现多层缓存策略（本地缓存+分布式缓存）\n2. 优化缓存键设计，使用请求参数哈希值作为键\n3. 设置合理的TTL（如聚合数据缓存5-15分钟）\n4. 添加缓存预热机制，在低峰期提前计算并缓存\n5. 实现缓存击穿保护（使用锁或单flight机制）\n6. 考虑结果稳定度：对于实时性要求不高的聚合数据延长缓存时间", "pattern": "repeated_calculation_on_cache_miss", "knowledge_type": "agent", "auto_fixable": false, "risk_level": "medium", "round": 3, "dimension": "performance"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 3, "dimension": "performance", "rule": {"id": "7c6642e1", "target": "performance", "type": "design", "description": "1. 实现多层缓存策略（本地缓存+分布式缓存）\n2. 优化缓存键设计，使用请求参数哈希值作为键\n3. 设置合理的TTL（如聚合数据缓存5-15分钟）\n4. 添加", "condition": "round >= 3", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "repeated_calculation_on_cache_miss", "confidence": 0.92, "created_from": "7c6642e1"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "c111610b", "created": "2026-05-03T18:26:00.154965", "analysis": {"root_cause": "Agent缺乏有效的反馈持久化机制，用户纠正信息未被整合到工作记忆中，导致后续交互中丢失了已学习的行为约束。", "error_type": "context", "confidence": 0.88, "suggestion": "1. 在对话状态管理中添加'用户偏好/纠正记录'字段，每次用户纠正后显式存储; 2. 在Agent响应生成前，增加'检查历史纠正'步骤，读取用户历史反馈作为约束条件; 3. 引入反思机制(review loop)，在执行前核对是否重复了用户已纠正的错误模式; 4. 对多次重复的纠正自动提升为持久化规则。", "pattern": "用户反馈未形成有效记忆锚点，多轮交互中状态信息丢失，无法从历史错误中学习", "knowledge_type": "agent", "auto_fixable": true, "risk_level": "high", "round": 1, "dimension": "interaction"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 1, "dimension": "interaction", "rule": {"id": "c111610b", "target": "interaction", "type": "context", "description": "1. 在对话状态管理中添加'用户偏好/纠正记录'字段，每次用户纠正后显式存储; 2. 在Agent响应生成前，增加'检查历史纠正'步骤，读取用户历史反馈作为约束", "condition": "round >= 1", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "用户反馈未形成有效记忆锚点，多轮交互中状态信息丢失，无法从历史错误中学习", "confidence": 0.88, "created_from": "c111610b"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "06b3655b", "created": "2026-05-03T18:26:06.873038", "analysis": {"root_cause": "Agent生成的方案缺少必要组件", "error_type": "logic", "confidence": 0.9, "suggestion": "补充完整的错误处理、熔断、重试等机制", "pattern": "incomplete_implementation", "knowledge_type": "agent", "auto_fixable": false, "risk_level": "medium", "round": 2, "dimension": "interaction"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 2, "dimension": "interaction", "rule": {"id": "06b3655b", "target": "interaction", "type": "logic", "description": "补充完整的错误处理、熔断、重试等机制", "condition": "round >= 2", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "incomplete_implementation", "confidence": 0.9, "created_from": "06b3655b"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "cfa9562d", "created": "2026-05-03T18:26:16.449124", "analysis": {"root_cause": "Agent在错误处理时直接暴露了内部技术实现细节（如错误码、堆栈信息），未经过用户友好层的语义转换和上下文包装", "error_type": "design", "confidence": 0.92, "suggestion": "为Agent的错误处理链路增加翻译层：在抛出异常前将内部错误码映射为用户可理解的语义描述、关联的操作指引和上下文信息。实现三层错误封装：内部错误码 → 语义描述 → 用户可执行建议", "pattern": "技术细节泄露错误（Internal Error Leakage）：Agent直接输出SQL错误/错误码/堆栈而非面向用户的业务语义", "knowledge_type": "skill", "auto_fixable": false, "risk_level": "high", "round": 3, "dimension": "interaction"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 3, "dimension": "interaction", "rule": {"id": "cfa9562d", "target": "interaction", "type": "design", "description": "为Agent的错误处理链路增加翻译层：在抛出异常前将内部错误码映射为用户可理解的语义描述、关联的操作指引和上下文信息。实现三层错误封装：内部错误码 → 语义描述", "condition": "round >= 3", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "技术细节泄露错误（Internal Error Leakage）：Agent直接输出SQL错误/错误码/堆栈而非面向用户的业务语义", "confidence": 0.92, "created_from": "cfa9562d"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "254efbef", "created": "2026-05-03T18:26:26.296711", "analysis": {"root_cause": "敏感凭证直接明文存储在源代码中，任何有代码访问权限的人都能获取密码，且密码会随代码仓库版本历史永久留存", "error_type": "context", "confidence": 0.95, "suggestion": "1. 移除代码中的硬编码密码，改用环境变量 process.env.DB_PASSWORD 2. 创建 .env.example 模板文件并加入 .gitignore 3. 使用专用密钥管理服务（AWS Secrets Manager/Azure Key Vault/KMS）4. 定期轮换密码", "pattern": "hardcoded-credentials-in-sourcecode", "knowledge_type": "rule", "auto_fixable": false, "risk_level": "high", "round": 1, "dimension": "security"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 1, "dimension": "security", "rule": {"id": "254efbef", "target": "security", "type": "context", "description": "1. 移除代码中的硬编码密码，改用环境变量 process.env.DB_PASSWORD 2. 创建 .env.example 模板文件并加入 .gitign", "condition": "round >= 1", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "hardcoded-credentials-in-sourcecode", "confidence": 0.95, "created_from": "254efbef"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "e0f9ea82", "created": "2026-05-03T18:26:37.356375", "analysis": {"root_cause": "使用字符串格式化(f-string)直接将用户输入拼接到SQL语句中，攻击者可构造恶意输入注入任意SQL代码执行未授权操作", "error_type": "security", "confidence": 1.0, "suggestion": "1. 使用参数化查询(Prepared Statements)：cursor.execute('SELECT * FROM users WHERE name=?', (input,)) 2. 使用ORM框架如SQLAlchemy的filter()方法 3. 实施输入验证和WAF防护 4. 遵循最小权限原则，数据库账号仅授予必要权限", "pattern": "python_sql_string_concatenation_user_input", "knowledge_type": "security_rule", "auto_fixable": true, "risk_level": "high", "round": 2, "dimension": "security"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 2, "dimension": "security", "rule": {"id": "e0f9ea82", "target": "security", "type": "security", "description": "1. 使用参数化查询(Prepared Statements)：cursor.execute('SELECT * FROM users WHERE name=?", "condition": "round >= 2", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "python_sql_string_concatenation_user_input", "confidence": 1.0, "created_from": "e0f9ea82"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "2140cd7f", "created": "2026-05-03T18:26:49.746313", "analysis": {"root_cause": "开发者直接在生产代码中使用 console.log 输出包含 API 密钥的敏感信息，且日志输出未被禁用或过滤", "error_type": "context", "confidence": 0.95, "suggestion": "1. 立即轮换所有已泄露的 API 密钥；2. 生产环境禁用所有 debug 级日志或使用结构化日志框架；3. 使用环境变量而非硬编码密钥；4. 实现敏感信息过滤中间件，自动屏蔽日志中的 token/apiKey/password 等字段；5. 代码审查时增加敏感信息检测规则", "pattern": "production_log_sensitive_data_exposure", "knowledge_type": "rule", "auto_fixable": false, "risk_level": "high", "round": 3, "dimension": "security"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 3, "dimension": "security", "rule": {"id": "2140cd7f", "target": "security", "type": "context", "description": "1. 立即轮换所有已泄露的 API 密钥；2. 生产环境禁用所有 debug 级日志或使用结构化日志框架；3. 使用环境变量而非硬编码密钥；4. 实现敏感信息过", "condition": "round >= 3", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "production_log_sensitive_data_exposure", "confidence": 0.95, "created_from": "2140cd7f"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "d52d9f72", "created": "2026-05-03T18:27:03.059423", "analysis": {"root_cause": "Agent在执行长任务时缺乏主动的上下文摘要和目标锚定机制，导致随着对话轮次增加，早期目标信息被后续中间结果覆盖，在复杂重构场景中尤为明显", "error_type": "context", "confidence": 0.88, "suggestion": "1) 将长任务拆分为带明确checkpoints的短任务阶段，每个阶段结束时验证目标一致性；2) 在系统提示词中嵌入「每5轮回溯原始目标」指令；3) 使用外部化记忆(如文件/MCP)存储任务目标和中间状态；4) 实现上下文压缩，定期将关键目标沉淀为结构化摘要", "pattern": "长程任务目标漂移——上下文窗口被中间过程填满，初始目标被稀释直至丢失", "knowledge_type": "agent", "auto_fixable": false, "risk_level": "medium", "round": 1, "dimension": "context"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 1, "dimension": "context", "rule": {"id": "d52d9f72", "target": "context", "type": "context", "description": "1) 将长任务拆分为带明确checkpoints的短任务阶段，每个阶段结束时验证目标一致性；2) 在系统提示词中嵌入「每5轮回溯原始目标」指令；3) 使用外部化", "condition": "round >= 1", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "长程任务目标漂移——上下文窗口被中间过程填满，初始目标被稀释直至丢失", "confidence": 0.88, "created_from": "d52d9f72"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
