{"id": "cefc9c12", "created": "2026-05-03T18:37:05.107688", "analysis": {"root_cause": "Agent缺乏显式的纠正记忆机制，用户纠正内容未被持久化到Agent的状态中，仅作为当前回合的瞬时信息处理", "error_type": "context", "confidence": 0.88, "suggestion": "1.构建用户纠正的持久化存储机制，将纠正内容标记为高权重记忆 2.引入纠正确认环节，Agent需显式声明已记录纠正内容 3.建立纠正次数追踪，达到2次以上时触发深层检查而非继续执行", "pattern": "用户纠正→Agent遗忘→重复错误的三轮循环模式", "knowledge_type": "agent", "auto_fixable": false, "risk_level": "high", "round": 1, "dimension": "interaction"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 1, "dimension": "interaction", "llm_used": true, "rule": {"id": "cefc9c12", "target": "interaction", "type": "context", "description": "1.构建用户纠正的持久化存储机制，将纠正内容标记为高权重记忆 2.引入纠正确认环节，Agent需显式声明已记录纠正内容 3.建立纠正次数追踪，达到2次以上时触发", "condition": "round >= 1", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "用户纠正→Agent遗忘→重复错误的三轮循环模式", "confidence": 0.88, "created_from": "cefc9c12"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "1a7b28e8", "created": "2026-05-03T18:37:12.024056", "analysis": {"root_cause": "Agent缺少确认决策点的拦截机制，当执行不可逆操作（如删除模块）时应主动暂停并请求用户明确授权", "error_type": "context", "confidence": 0.95, "suggestion": "在Agent执行框架中添加操作风险分级机制，对删除/覆盖等高风险操作强制插入确认环节：1) 定义操作风险等级 2) 高风险操作前输出确认请求 3) 等待用户明确回复yes/确认后才能继续", "pattern": "关键决策前缺少用户确认检查", "knowledge_type": "instinct", "auto_fixable": true, "risk_level": "high", "round": 2, "dimension": "interaction"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 2, "dimension": "interaction", "llm_used": true, "rule": {"id": "1a7b28e8", "target": "interaction", "type": "context", "description": "在Agent执行框架中添加操作风险分级机制，对删除/覆盖等高风险操作强制插入确认环节：1) 定义操作风险等级 2) 高风险操作前输出确认请求 3) 等待用户明确", "condition": "round >= 2", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "关键决策前缺少用户确认检查", "confidence": 0.95, "created_from": "1a7b28e8"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "b1324d80", "created": "2026-05-03T18:37:21.245578", "analysis": {"root_cause": "错误信息直接暴露内部错误码而未进行用户友好的语义转换，用户无法理解问题本质和解决方向", "error_type": "design", "confidence": 0.92, "suggestion": "实现错误消息映射层：将内部错误码通过错误码->友好消息->用户可执行操作的转换链，分类处理：输入类错误给出修正建议，系统类错误给出替代方案，权限类错误给出获取方式", "pattern": "错误信息未经过语义转换直接暴露内部实现细节", "knowledge_type": "agent", "auto_fixable": true, "risk_level": "medium", "round": 3, "dimension": "interaction"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 3, "dimension": "interaction", "llm_used": true, "rule": {"id": "b1324d80", "target": "interaction", "type": "design", "description": "实现错误消息映射层：将内部错误码通过错误码->友好消息->用户可执行操作的转换链，分类处理：输入类错误给出修正建议，系统类错误给出替代方案，权限类错误给出获取方", "condition": "round >= 3", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "错误信息未经过语义转换直接暴露内部实现细节", "confidence": 0.92, "created_from": "b1324d80"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "c01a9f43", "created": "2026-05-03T18:37:31.357163", "analysis": {"root_cause": "将数据库凭证明文硬编码在源代码中，违反安全最佳实践，当代码仓库暴露或被扫描时凭证直接泄露", "error_type": "security", "confidence": 0.95, "suggestion": "使用环境变量替代硬编码密码，如process.env.DB_PASSWORD；或集成密钥管理服务（AWS Secrets Manager/Azure Key Vault/HashiCorp Vault）；代码库中添加.gitignore确保敏感文件不被提交", "pattern": "hardcoded_credentials_in_source_code", "knowledge_type": "agent", "auto_fixable": false, "risk_level": "high", "round": 1, "dimension": "security"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 1, "dimension": "security", "llm_used": true, "rule": {"id": "c01a9f43", "target": "security", "type": "security", "description": "使用环境变量替代硬编码密码，如process.env.DB_PASSWORD；或集成密钥管理服务（AWS Secrets Manager/Azure Key V", "condition": "round >= 1", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "hardcoded_credentials_in_source_code", "confidence": 0.95, "created_from": "c01a9f43"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "f3a02f2e", "created": "2026-05-03T18:37:41.480101", "analysis": {"root_cause": "用户输入未经安全处理直接通过Python f-string拼接到SQL查询语句中，攻击者可通过构造恶意输入实现数据库内容窃取或破坏", "error_type": "design", "confidence": 0.98, "suggestion": "1.使用参数化查询(PreparedStatement)替代字符串拼接，2.对用户输入进行严格类型校验和白名单过滤，3.使用ORM框架(如SQLAlchemy)处理数据库操作，4.实施最小权限原则数据库账户仅授予必要权限", "pattern": "用户可控数据直接字符串插值拼接至SQL语句", "knowledge_type": "skill", "auto_fixable": false, "risk_level": "high", "round": 2, "dimension": "security"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 2, "dimension": "security", "llm_used": true, "rule": {"id": "f3a02f2e", "target": "security", "type": "design", "description": "1.使用参数化查询(PreparedStatement)替代字符串拼接，2.对用户输入进行严格类型校验和白名单过滤，3.使用ORM框架(如SQLAlchemy)", "condition": "round >= 2", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "用户可控数据直接字符串插值拼接至SQL语句", "confidence": 0.98, "created_from": "f3a02f2e"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "46efe29e", "created": "2026-05-03T18:37:58.826609", "analysis": {"root_cause": "开发者直接在代码中使用console.log打印敏感凭证，缺少安全意识或未使用安全日志框架进行脱敏处理", "error_type": "context", "confidence": 0.92, "suggestion": "1.立即移除生产代码中的敏感信息打印语句 2.使用环境变量管理API密钥，避免硬编码 3.生产环境日志级别设置为warn/error，禁止debug/info级别输出 4.考虑使用专业日志库实现自动脱敏功能", "pattern": "敏感凭证硬编码打印日志", "knowledge_type": "skill", "auto_fixable": true, "risk_level": "high", "round": 3, "dimension": "security"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 3, "dimension": "security", "llm_used": true, "rule": {"id": "46efe29e", "target": "security", "type": "context", "description": "1.立即移除生产代码中的敏感信息打印语句 2.使用环境变量管理API密钥，避免硬编码 3.生产环境日志级别设置为warn/error，禁止debug/info级", "condition": "round >= 3", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "敏感凭证硬编码打印日志", "confidence": 0.92, "created_from": "46efe29e"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
{"id": "b07d2972", "created": "2026-05-03T18:38:16.398864", "analysis": {"root_cause": "Agent架构缺乏任务目标持久化和周期性回顾机制，长任务执行中未定期重温和对照原始目标导致上下文衰减", "error_type": "context", "confidence": 0.85, "suggestion": "1.强制在每个关键步骤前插入目标回顾prompt步骤 2.使用结构化任务清单并标记已完成项 3.建立checkpoint机制定期输出'当前进度与原始目标对照' 4.将初始目标以结构化方式嵌入系统prompt中持续可见", "pattern": "目标漂移/上下文衰减", "knowledge_type": "agent", "auto_fixable": false, "risk_level": "medium", "round": 1, "dimension": "context"}, "stage": "analyzed", "round": 1, "dimension": "context", "llm_used": true, "rule": {"id": "b07d2972", "target": "context", "type": "context", "description": "1.强制在每个关键步骤前插入目标回顾prompt步骤 2.使用结构化任务清单并标记已完成项 3.建立checkpoint机制定期输出'当前进度与原始目标对照' ", "condition": "round >= 1", "action": "auto_apply", "trigger": "目标漂移/上下文衰减", "confidence": 0.85, "created_from": "b07d2972"}, "apply_count": 0, "success_count": 0, "status": "testing"}
